  volumenAudio: 0.8
  textoFragmento: "Child.\r\nMittens?\u2026\r\nSo you\u2019re still around, huh?\r\nDon\u2019t
    think I\u2019ve forgotten all the scares you gave me, little furball\u2026 I
    almost gave a heart attack.\r\nAlright, alright\u2026 peace between us.\r\nI\u2019ll
    bring you some food every day, deal?\r\nBut promise me you won\u2019t give me
    away next time there\u2019s a witch around.\r\nDeal, Mittens.\r"
